summary:
“杰西·卡兔”女士，你知道的，我尝试制作了她的舞台服装。
"Jessica Rabbit" lady, you know, I tried to make her stage costumes.
descriptionHtml:
啊·· 我并不擅长英语
Ah. I'm not good at English.

“sleepytigereyes”发布了一位叫“杰西·卡兔”的性感女郎，非常凑巧的是，我最近完成了“杰西·卡兔”女士的舞台服装。
"Sleepytigereyes" released a sexy girl called "Jessica Rabbit" in "nexusmods", and it happened that I recently finished the stage dress of "Jessica Rabbit".

在部分朋友的期盼下，我决定分享我制作的MOD。
In the hope of some friends, I decided to share my MOD.

我并不是非常专业的模型师，它可能存在一点点小问题。希望你喜欢它。
Unfortunately,I am not a very professional modeler,It may have some minor ailments. I hope you like it.

免费基础模型是从“www.deviantart.com”获取，请不要将本MOD用于任何商业用途。
The free basic model is obtained from "www.deviantart.com". Please do not use this MOD for any commercial purpose.

MOD需求(MOD requirements)：
你至少拥有“UNP”类型身体与皮肤(You have at least the "UNP" type of body and skin)
XP32 Maximum Skeleton - XPMS
HDT Physics Extensions

高跟鞋是“Frankfranky”的作品，你可以在这里找到它(High heels are works of "Frankfranky". You can find them here)：
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89613

如果你需要"CBBE bodyslide"， "sleepytigereyes"已经完成了它们，非常感谢 "sleepytigereyes" !
If you need "CBBE bodyslide", "sleepytigereyes" has already completed them. Thank you very much for "sleepytigereyes" !
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92895
